message: Aded a similar reference repeatedly noted in Land of charity by Samuel Mateer and "History of the london missionary society" by "RICHARD LOVETT M A". RICHARD LOVETT M A.Similar observations by Samuel Mateer and Richard Lovett give a very vivid picture of the period when the caste system existed.This will help more to history students and historians
Included a reference link of the book
The land of charity is an old book which was written by Rev Samuel Mateer F L S about 18 century kerala, says a one line clarification about cast system among the hindu communities in kerala
Included a new information from an old book
They have connection with brahmins. So dont spread lies...
Re included history which was erased by others
Included history of vishwakarmas from texts
